                <p class="text-muted">See what our customers have to say about their experience.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="d-flex gap-10 col-md-6 col-lg-7 col-xl-9">

                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between h-100">
                        <p>
                            MoneyMind helped me save $500 in just 3 months. It’s a game changer!
                        </p>
