                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="mb-0">Sarah L.</h6>
                                <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Freelance Designer
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between h-100">
                        <p>
                            The budgeting tools are so intuitive. I finally feel in control of my money.
                        </p>
                        <div class="text-warning mb-4">
                            <i class="bx bxs-star"></i>
                            <i class="bx bxs-star"></i>
                            <i class="bx bxs-star"></i>
                            <i class="bx bxs-star"></i>
                            <i class="bx bxs-star"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                            <div class="avatar me-3 avatar-sm">
                                <img src="~/assets/images/avatars/james.png" alt="Avatar" class="rounded-circle">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h6 class="mb-0">James W.</h6>
                                <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Software Engineer</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body text-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between h-100">
